> ## Walkthrough
> 
> This change updates the MCP protocol version constant, removes a local constant in the StreamableHTTP client transport in favor of using the protocol package's constant, and introduces a new StreamableHTTPServer implementation with comprehensive tests. It also adds a minimal logging utility and removes the previously introduced StreamableHTTPOption interface and stub server from HTTP transport options. Additionally, it refactors the SSE server configuration to use functional options and updates example programs to replace SSE transport with the new StreamableHTTP transport.
